messages.title: Surge in Support here for Lib Dems
messages.content: The result of the last General Election shows that only the Liberal Democrats are gaining ground to challenge the Tories in North West Cambridgeshire. Kevin Wilkins has served on Cambridgeshire County Council for many years and knows our area well.
